fields.name: What I think about this.
fields.value: I'm in Northern California. If you once liked TFG, you need therapy. If you still like TFG, you may well have a 12 step program in your future.

fields.name: More thinking.
fields.value: If you think you are a conservative rebel, you're not. You're called a reactionary autocrat. If you seek a redux of the civil war, think again. We will remove your statehood, keep you as a territory.
